dget\">\n	<p style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Ocean Edu Vietnam is the leading english center in Vietnam for more than 10 years with more than 30 branches nationwide in more than 22 different cities across the country and is still growing.Ocean Edu is a trademark of JSC Ocean Education in Vietnam.</p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Ocean edu is a proud educational institution invested by Lincoln School Management of Singapore. Ocean Edu has more than 200 experienced and qualified foreign teachers and more than 600 Vietnamese Staff that is serving more than 50,000 students across north Vietnam.</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Ocean Edu English Centers provides students , teachers and employees with an excellent study and work environment as it is fully built and equipped to the highest standards. Ocean Edu uses the latest state-of-the-art teaching technologies such as the smartboard, smartTv to engage our students. Ocean Edu Classrooms are fully independent and equipped with teaching materials, air-conditioned with wifi and internet access.</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Ocean Edu Teachers are also equipped with teaching resources like Online and Offline Itools, Dvd\'s, Computers, printers, that they can access to prepare for their classes.</p></div>\n</div></div></div><div id=\"pgc-82-0-2\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.2584089390903\" ><div id=\"panel-82-0-2-0\" class=\"widget_text so-panel widget widget_custom_html panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"2\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"textwidget custom-html-widget\"><div class = \"sidebar-custom\">\n<ul id = \"navigation\">\n<li class =\"active\"><a href =\"#\">Introduction to Ocean Edu</a></li>\n<li><a href =\"#\">Why Work at Ocean Edu</a></li>\n<li><a href =\"#\">Branch Locations</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>', 'Ocean Edu Introduction', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ocean-edu-introduction', '', '', 